snippet.title: 7 Minutes in Hell Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey there, Thrill-Seekers! Welcome to 7 Minutes in Hell, the livestream gameshow where contestants risk big to win big! Enter the challenge arena, and face off against terrifying monsters, obstacles, and traps under the watchful eye of your host JRDarkX! Contestants have 7 Minutes to snatch as much loot and valuables as they can, before making their daring escape. If you survive, you can try your luck and come back for even more danger and even juicier rewards!

Early Access Out Now on Steam!

#7MinutesinHell #7MIH #Indie #gaming #GaggleStudios
Brought to you by @GaggleStudios
